---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Blog — Nachiket Kulkarni"
  description="Blog by Nachiket Kulkarni on DevOps, MLOps, Kubernetes, and platform engineering."
>
  <div class="page">
    <h1 class="page-title">Blog</h1>
    <p class="page-subtitle">Thoughts on DevOps, MLOps, and platform engineering</p>

    <div class="coming-soon">
      <div class="cs-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M12 20h9"/>
          <path d="M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h2>Coming Soon</h2>
      <p>I'm working on some articles. Here's what's planned:</p>

      <ul class="planned-posts">
        <li>
          <span class="post-bullet">→</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Building an MLOps pipeline from scratch</strong>
            <p>End-to-end ML workflow: data ingestion, training, versioning, serving, and monitoring on Kubernetes.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="post-bullet">→</span>
          <div>
            <strong>GitOps with ArgoCD and Kyverno</strong>
            <p>How to manage Kubernetes deployments declaratively with policy enforcement and automated drift detection.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="post-bullet">→</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Agentic AI for DevOps automation</strong>
            <p>Exploring LLM-powered agents for incident response, runbook automation, and infrastructure management.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <p class="subscribe-note">
        In the meantime, connect with me on <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/nkulkarni9493" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a> or check out my projects on <a href="https://github.com/nachikul" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .coming-soon {
    max-width: 640px;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  .cs-icon {
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .coming-soon h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .coming-soon > p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .planned-posts {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .planned-posts li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.25rem;
    transition: border-color 0.15s;
  }

  .planned-posts li:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .post-bullet {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 0.1rem;
  }

  .planned-posts strong {
    display: block;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .planned-posts p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .subscribe-note {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
</style>
